~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : revshout                                  ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : revshout

   This command allows you to review the "shout" buffer, displaying to you
   the last few shouts in the talker.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : shout, shemote, review, revtell
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
